snippet.title: TF2 Classic - 2.1.3 Patch Trailer
snippet.description:
The 2.1.3 Patch for TF2 Classic is out now! Featuring a brand new map, new player shading, weapon reworks and adjustments, map revisions, additions for mappers... you get the point. There's a lot!

Learn more at: https://tf2classic.com/?id=6464
